#: ../../docs/classes/class_color.rst:10
msgid "Color"
msgstr "Color"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_color.rst:12
msgid "Color in RGBA format with some support for ARGB format."
msgstr "RGBA格式的颜色，并支持ARGB格式。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_color.rst:15
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_color.rst:17
msgid ""
"A color is represented by red, green, and blue ``(r, g, b)`` components. "
"Additionally, ``a`` represents the alpha component, often used for "
"transparency. Values are in floating-point and usually range from 0 to 1."
" Some properties (such as :ref:`CanvasItem.modulate "
"<class_CanvasItem_property_modulate>`) may accept values greater than 1."
msgstr ""
"颜色由红色、绿色和蓝色 ``(r, g, b)`` 组成部分表示。另外，``a`` "
"代表alpha成分，通常用于透明度。值以浮点数表示，通常为0到1。某些属性（例如， :ref:`CanvasItem.modulate "
"<class_CanvasItem_property_modulate>`）可以接受大于1的值。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_color.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can also create a color from standardized color names by using "
":ref:`@GDScript.ColorN <class_@GDScript_method_ColorN>` or directly using"
" the color constants defined here. The standardized color set is based on"
" the `X11 color names <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X11_color_names>`_."
msgstr ""

